<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/642328-why-not-read-the-false-crises-of-rachel">Why not read &quot;The False Crises of Rachel Carson: Silent Spring at 50&quot; for a critique of this badly flawed book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_642328'><a id="like_count_community_question_642328" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/642328?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F27333.Silent_Spring">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/642328-why-not-read-the-false-crises-of-rachel">5 years ago</a>
