<div id="review_1894355315" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1894355315" />
    <a title="TXGAL1" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5418447-txgal1"><img alt="TXGAL1" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1471219772p2/5418447.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1894355315?book_show_action=true">Mar 29, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="TXGAL1" class="user" itemprop="url" name="TXGAL1" href="/user/show/5418447-txgal1">TXGAL1</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5418447-txgal1?shelf=nonfiction">nonfiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1894355315" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8867739202961782711">Astonishing and terrifying. Although this book was written in 1962, we still use chemicals in our daily lives without enough thought. <br/><br/>Asthma has been shown in some studies to be caused by the occurrence of cockroaches; but, what if it was in fact caused by the inhalation of chemicals used to eradicate the pests?<br/><br/>Could chemicals sprayed in our neighborhoods, in our homes, etc. be the true cause of autism? <br/><br/>Very thought provoking book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


